      *              * Controllo esito richiamo modulo                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        s-liv                =    zero
                     move  "#"            to   w-cnt-dic-ini-pgm
           else      move  spaces         to   w-cnt-dic-ini-pgm      .
       dic-ini-pgm-999.
           exit.

