      *                      * da stampare : ad uscita                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-stp-t01-inx-lin    >    w-stp-t01-ctr-lin
                     go to prn-liv-det-s01-260.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Interlinea                              *
