           move      "A"                  to   p-tip                  .
           move      28                   to   p-car                  .
           move      p-lnr                to   p-lin                  .
           move      104                  to   p-pos                  .
           move      w-stp-t01-col-004
                    (w-stp-t01-inx-lin)   to   p-alf                  .
