                                         using p                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Interlinea                                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "VP"                 to   p-ope                  .
           add       2
                     p-lnr              giving p-lin                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
       int-pag-sta-scb-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
